The paper proposes a new model for high-dimensional sparse regression, which is a common problem in machine learning and statistics. The paper also focuses on the robustness of the proposed model, which is an important topic in many areas of computer science. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.ST (Statistics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
